        "rich_text_wJrEPV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Engagement Ring: Engraving Ideas That Mean Something</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_jtcaET": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_74wywU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>An Engagement Ring is a symbol of love. Choosing an Engagement Ring is already a big moment, the metal, the diamond, the setting, the whole deal. While the sparkle of a diamond catches the eye, it’s the engraving on the inside of the band that can capture the heart. </p><p>These subtle, hidden messages are private, often seen only by the couple, and hold a deeper emotional value. If you're looking to personalize your <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Engagement Rings\">Engagement Ring</a> with something truly meaningful, here are some engraving ideas that go beyond the ordinary.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_GhEarX": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_d9d8a2c8-ffaf-43a8-bd60-76d52db7c288.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9gYA8F": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. The Classics that Never Fail",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1. The Classics that Never Fail</h2><p>A classic message confessing your love and commitment to your partner can be the perfect inscription. Phrases like “I love you” or “Yours forever” are timeless and will always be a reminder of your love to your partner. You can personalise this even more by adding your initials.</p>",
            "custom_id": "classics"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xMjxKW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2. A Date You’ll Always Remember",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>2. A Date You’ll Always Remember</h2><p>Simple, timeless, and deeply personal, engraving an important date adds a unique timestamp to your love story. It could be anything, the date you first saw them or the date you plan to get married on. These engravings serve as milestones, reminding you both of how far you’ve come and where you’re headed.</p>",
            "custom_id": "date"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Qzqpti": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. A Quote That Feels Like You",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>3. A Quote That Feels Like You</h2><p>Every couple speaks their own language, some inside jokes, sayings that have a special meaning, a movie line that both of you love. All of these make for a perfect engraving, representing the unique love you have for each other.</p>",
            "custom_id": "quote"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_C9QFga": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Fingerprints or Soundwaves",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>4. Fingerprints or Soundwaves</h2><p>Looking for something ultra-personal and unique? You can now etch your fingerprint on your beloved’s ring to let them know you are always with them. You can even engrave the soundwaves of you favourite song or of a voice recording.</p>",
            "custom_id": "fingerprints"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_NWyWxb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Where It All Started",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>5. Where It All Started</h2><p>Every love story has a place. Maybe it was a coffee shop, a beach, or a street corner you’ll never forget. You can engrave the coordinates of that exact spot. It's subtle, secretive, and sentimental, ideal for couples who want to keep the meaning between just the two of them.</p><p>It’s subtle. It’s meaningful. It’s yours.</p>",
            "custom_id": "where"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_4gUnMp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Something Spiritual",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>6. Something Spiritual</h2><p>If your relationship is grounded in faith or spirituality, an engraving can reflect that side of your journey, too. A short verse or blessing adds meaning beyond just the two of you.</p>",
            "custom_id": "spiritual"
          }
        }
      },
